Database used:- ES, postGIS(not sure present in existing architecture)
Have the info for all the police station data:- static
User data:- dynamic(changes while executing the solution)
flag:- to know the status of user(emergency||normal)




Kafka/mqtt(input data:-(userData&& flag))---------->ES(update userdata constantly in ES) ---------->(if flag is true:- send message to nearby police coordinate)


Fields
id: userID/policeId
name:String
type:Police/User
alert: boolean
location: geo_point(lat,lon)
time: current Time
